Pyrophosphate-energized proton pump (EC 3.6.1.1) (Pyrophosphate-
energized inorganic pyrophosphatase) (H+-PPase) (Membrane-bound
proton-translocating pyrophosphatase).
"A pyrophosphate synthase gene: molecular cloning and sequencing of
